---
title: Swedish-Inspired Bacon Burgers with Potato Coins and Dilly Mayo
description: You don't need to buy build-it-yourself furniture to get a taste of Swedish meatballs for dinner! This cheeky burger is cloaked in a creamy mushroom sauce with some potato coins and dilly dip on the side.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burgers-au-bacon-facon-suedoise-26939b7a.jpg
